data.description: Welcome to this exquisite almost new home nestled in the sought-after River Bend subdivision of Tarpon Springs. Conveniently located near the vibrant Sponge Docks, boating opportunities, marinas, restaurants, fishing spots, and water sports; this centrally positioned residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and leisure. This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has been meticulous maintained and offers a spacious floor plan, allowing natural light to permeate every corner through the abundant windows. Indulge in the premium features and finishes throughout this home, including stunning vinyl wood-look flooring, quartz countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless-steel appliances complete with a generous center island with ample cabinet storage. The master suite provides a tranquil sanctuary, featuring a spacious walk-in closet, dual vanities, and a luxurious glass-enclosed shower. The two additional bedrooms offer generous dimensions and abundant natural light, accompanied by ample closet space. The covered patio extends out to the yard with beautiful pavers offering a hot tub and creates an idyllic setting for al fresco dining and relaxation with friends and family. For boating enthusiasts, this property is perfectly situated near multiple boat ramps, granting effortless access to the nearby waterways. Immerse yourself in the vibrant culture and entertainment of Tarpon Springs, with the renowned Sponge Docks just a short drive away. Downtown Tarpon Springs awaits with its charming assortment of shops, cafes, and art galleries, adding a touch of elegance to your everyday life. Embrace the opportunity to own this stunning newer construction home that effortlessly blends luxury with convenience. You will also enjoy the perk of the solar panels for a very inexpensive electric bill. Schedule your private showing today.
